creator: Risingson
descriptionHtml:
Interactive map system and chain mapping for Eve Online.

The app is capable of tracking your ingame location and setting waypoints to the Eve client. When jumping wormholes the maps get extended by those connections. Going deeper into w-space will switch to a chain map view.

Multiple API data options and layers can be combined to display on the maps.

Tap solarsystems or wormhole-connection lines for options.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fix for pasting share-group codes
Other minor fixes and improvements

title: Eveeye for EVE Online

creator: Risingson
descriptionHtml:
Interactive map system and chain mapping for Eve Online.

Features
- Travel and tactical companion of New Eden
- Search for places, stations or agents
- Get comprehensive Info on solarsystems
- Chain-mapping including connected k-space
- Share data with your fellow pilots
- Configure your maps to display live data
- Track your ingame location
- Set Waypoints to the eve client
- Find Routes using your chain, jumpbridges and Thera
- Plan jumpdrive routes
- Plot your Jump-range

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Jump planning + minor fixes and improvements.
You might need to re-auth your characters.
